  "detailed_description": "<strong>HELIX</strong> is a single player platform action game. Use your special skill of changing gravity and go on a platform adventure of a lifetime. Go fast as you can by upgrading your character and try not to die by dangerous spikes.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Change your gravity</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1620800/extras/7002606f08499023e6d402bd4e2108e5.poster.avif?t=1702620898\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1620800/extras/7002606f08499023e6d402bd4e2108e5.webm?t=1702620898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1620800/extras/7002606f08499023e6d402bd4e2108e5.mp4?t=1702620898\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Change your gravity to beat the level by the ways you would have not imagined.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Upgrade your character</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1620800/extras/3b522254ab38aa35e64ee8fc5ee0eaad.poster.avif?t=1702620898\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1620800/extras/3b522254ab38aa35e64ee8fc5ee0eaad.webm?t=1702620898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1620800/extras/3b522254ab38aa35e64ee8fc5ee0eaad.mp4?t=1702620898\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You can upgrade your character with the coins that you collected and make your character gain more hearts or speeds to help you out on your great platform adventure.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Assist Mode</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1620800/extras/b47dfd81e23ff94fefd654c891a0e70c.poster.avif?t=1702620898\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1620800/extras/b47dfd81e23ff94fefd654c891a0e70c.webm?t=1702620898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1620800/extras/b47dfd81e23ff94fefd654c891a0e70c.mp4?t=1702620898\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Is game too hard for you? Do not worry! WE have <strong>Assist Mode</strong> to help you out, if you use <strong>Assist Mode</strong>, the <strong>game over</strong> will be disabled so you can enjoy the game without any stress!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Die</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1620800/extras/a048038fecfe789cb98d5851a457374e.poster.avif?t=1702620898\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1620800/extras/a048038fecfe789cb98d5851a457374e.webm?t=1702620898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1620800/extras/a048038fecfe789cb98d5851a457374e.mp4?t=1702620898\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>If you lose all of your hearts during game you'll be sent back to level one and you'll lose all of your coins, so be careful what you do!",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>HELIX</strong> is a single player platform action game. Use your special skill of changing gravity and go on a platform adventure of a lifetime. Go fast as you can by upgrading your character and try not to die by dangerous spikes.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Change your gravity</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1620800/extras/7002606f08499023e6d402bd4e2108e5.poster.avif?t=1702620898\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1620800/extras/7002606f08499023e6d402bd4e2108e5.webm?t=1702620898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1620800/extras/7002606f08499023e6d402bd4e2108e5.mp4?t=1702620898\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Change your gravity to beat the level by the ways you would have not imagined.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Upgrade your character</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1620800/extras/3b522254ab38aa35e64ee8fc5ee0eaad.poster.avif?t=1702620898\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1620800/extras/3b522254ab38aa35e64ee8fc5ee0eaad.webm?t=1702620898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1620800/extras/3b522254ab38aa35e64ee8fc5ee0eaad.mp4?t=1702620898\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You can upgrade your character with the coins that you collected and make your character gain more hearts or speeds to help you out on your great platform adventure.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Assist Mode</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1620800/extras/b47dfd81e23ff94fefd654c891a0e70c.poster.avif?t=1702620898\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1620800/extras/b47dfd81e23ff94fefd654c891a0e70c.webm?t=1702620898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1620800/extras/b47dfd81e23ff94fefd654c891a0e70c.mp4?t=1702620898\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Is game too hard for you? Do not worry! WE have <strong>Assist Mode</strong> to help you out, if you use <strong>Assist Mode</strong>, the <strong>game over</strong> will be disabled so you can enjoy the game without any stress!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Die</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1620800/extras/a048038fecfe789cb98d5851a457374e.poster.avif?t=1702620898\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1620800/extras/a048038fecfe789cb98d5851a457374e.webm?t=1702620898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1620800/extras/a048038fecfe789cb98d5851a457374e.mp4?t=1702620898\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>If you lose all of your hearts during game you'll be sent back to level one and you'll lose all of your coins, so be careful what you do!",
